reviewText: Another great Movie for the years gone by.

Brilliant! Hadn't seen this since I was a kid. The movie really holds up well, there are only a couple of times when the effects look dated. Raquel... OMG, they do not make women like that any more... Smart, strong, fearless and still feminine.... Grrr baby Yeah!
I gave it to my Cardiologist and she enjoyed it.  This is a fifty year old movie.
This one is my favorite, I watych it over and over.
